-1 8 years, seven months.

01:14:05.501 --> 01:14:10.438
That'd be us, Ernie.
The Young Thundering Herd. l like it.

01:14:10.607 --> 01:14:12.768
Oh, l like that.
Do you mind if l use that?

01:14:12.942 --> 01:14:14.910
Hell, no. l'm already making T-shirts.

01:14:16.613 --> 01:14:18.740
What you think about this?

01:14:18.915 --> 01:14:21.509
''The Young Thundering Herd.''

01:14:22.118 --> 01:14:24.916
l like it, George!
Can you get me one of those?

01:14:31.728 --> 01:14:33.252
We've practiced.

01:14:38.001 --> 01:14:39.559
We have a plan.

01:14:43.373 --> 01:14:44.670
And now it's game day.

01:14:47.911 --> 01:14:50.345
Nate Ruffin,
are you the captain of this team?

01:14:50.513 --> 01:14:51.810
Yes, sir, l am, coach!

01:14:52.415 --> 01:14:55.077
Well, why don't you take us
onto that field?

01:14:56.653 --> 01:14:58.848
Everybody up! Come in here!

01:14:59.656 --> 01:15:04.355
Now, 60 minutes! We play till the whistle
blow! And you know how we do.

01:15:04.527 --> 01:15:06.051
-We are?
-Marshall!

01:15:06.229 --> 01:15:08.629
-Now, let's take it to the field!
-Yeah!

01:15:13.403 --> 01:15:16.668
<i>And here they come,</i>
<i>the Young Thundering Herd of Marshall!</i>

01:15:25.348 --> 01:15:27.714
