01:15:29.953 --> 01:15:31.420
Game day.

01:15:36.693 --> 01:15:39.685
<i>Welcome to Morehead, Kentucky,</i>
<i>where the Morehead State Eagles...</i>

01:15:39.862 --> 01:15:43.730
<i>...take on the Thundering Herd of Marshall</i>
<i>University in their 1 97 1 season opener.</i>

01:15:43.900 --> 01:15:47.267
<i>The Marshall Thundering Herd</i>
<i>was marked by tragedy last season...</i>

01:15:47.437 --> 01:15:50.463
<i>...but they are back in the saddle</i>
